	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Mapper 2 is good for 16 KB ROMs, but because $8000-$BFFF is undefined at power on, it's not for 32 KB ROMs unless you do a mapper write before reading $8000-$BFFF. BNROM is closer to the behavior of "mapper 0 without CHR ROM".

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


